<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.9.2">
<l>cūḻal palapala vallāṉ ṟollaiyaṅ kālat tulakai</l>
<l>kēḻaloṉ ṟākiyi ṭanta kēcava ṉeṉṉuṭai yammāṉ</l>
<l>vēḻa maruppaiyo cittāṉ viṇṇavark keṇṇa lariyā</l>
<l>ṉāḻa neṭuṅkaṭal cērntā ṉavaṉeṉ ṉarukali lāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who can encompass many many, Keśava who in old times</l>
<l>becoming a boar scooped up the world, my father,</l>
<l>the one who broke the elephant’s tusk, the one difficult to think for the celestials,</l>
<l>the one who joined the deep large sea, he is in my proximity.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
